Effective Date: [2025-08-17]

Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how VirAIs (“we,” “our,” “us”) collects, uses, and protects your information.

1. Information We Collect

Personal Information: Information you provide directly, such as your name, email, or account details.

Usage Data: Information about how you use VirAIs (e.g., interactions, settings, preferences).

Device Data: Information about your device, browser, or operating system.

2. How We Use Information

We use the information we collect to:

Provide, maintain, and improve VirAIs.

Communicate with you (e.g., updates, support).

Monitor usage and prevent abuse.

Comply with legal obligations.

3. Sharing of Information

We do not sell your personal information. We may share information with:

Service Providers who help us operate VirAIs.

Legal Authorities when required by law.

Business Transfers if VirAIs is merged, acquired, or sold.

4. Data Security

We use reasonable measures to protect your information. However, no system is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.

5. Your Choices

You may update or delete your account information at any time.

You may opt out of marketing emails by following unsubscribe instructions.

Depending on your location, you may have additional privacy rights under applicable law.

6. Children’s Privacy

VirAIs is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect information from children. If you believe a child has provided us data, please contact us.

7. Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted here, and continued use of VirAIs means you accept the updated policy.
